text: Thornfield is a Canadian racehorse. Thornfield may also refer to: * Thornfield Township, Ozark County, Missouri, an inactive township ** Thornfield, Missouri, United States, an unincorporated community * Thornfield Hall, a location in the novel Jane Eyre by Charlotte Bronte * Tara Thornfield, a character in the British soap opera Emmerdale
title: Thornfield (disambiguation)
